This error is produced by bson library (e.g. {{bson.checkKey}}). By deeper research:
- This behavior is controlled by {{checkKey}} option, that passed to bson.
- The checkKey option is set to {{false}} (which is OK) in [node-mongodb-native|https://github.com/mongodb/node-mongodb-native/blob/2.1/lib/db.js#L1014].
- But it is always set to {{true}} and passed options are ignored [here|https://github.com/christkv/mongodb-core/blob/1.3/lib/wireprotocol/3_2_support.js#L56] in mongodb-core.

Please suggest a solution on this issue.

